description: This unit is located in one of South Boston's premiere areas. Located on a quiet one way street and a five minute walk to Andrew Station. Just minutes away from Andrew Square and Dorchester Street filled with restaurants and shops.  A well maintained building offering, two generous bedrooms, an updated kitchen and bath, new wall to wall carpet. The roof was replaced in 2017 and the gas boiler was replaced in 2018. Low condo fee. Check out Washington Village brochure attached .
